    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is suitable for a buyer looking for a functional driver that needs some TLC. Mechanically, the engine starts and runs, though it would benefit from a comprehensive tune-up and inspection of the suspension components. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading in the clear coat on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear and staining, and some of the plastic trim pieces are loose. It is a solid candidate for a daily driver if you don't mind the cosmetic imperfections and are willing to put in a little work to bring it back to its best.",
