    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my trusty ride! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape, ready for plenty more adventures. It drives smoothly, looks great, and has been well-loved. If you're looking for a dependable car that's ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a prime example of BMW's engineering peak, featuring the S54 powerplant with its signature individual throttle bodies and high-RPM ceiling. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual and a factory limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes VANOS timing adjustment and chassis subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity under load. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics for exceptional turn-in and lateral stability. A mechanically honest machine for the serious driver looking for an analog performance icon.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Good condition. Runs well. Clean title. Regular maintenance performed. Minor cosmetic wear only. Reliable vehicle.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
