      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that perfectly captures the balance of performance and comfort. The exterior finish retains a high-gloss luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia\u2014typical for a car that has enjoyed the open road. The alloy wheels are clean, and the tires have ample tread remaining for many miles to come. Inside, the cabin is remarkably well-preserved; the leather seating is supple with no cracks or tears, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. All onboard electronics, including the navigation system, heated seats, and premium audio, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, reflecting a consistent service history. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension remains tight, providing a composed and quiet ride. This car has been smoke-free and garage-kept, serving as a reliable and stylish companion for its next owner.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical reliability and aesthetic discipline. This unit has been curated to ensure a superior driving experience, featuring a well-preserved interior and a robust powertrain that reflects a history of diligent maintenance. It offers an exceptional balance of performance and long-term value for the sophisticated buyer who demands excellence. We invite you to experience the integrity of this vehicle firsthand.",
