      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car, and it's been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect reliable companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. It runs great and is ready for its next adventure with a new owner! Feel free to message me if you have any questions or want to come see it in person.",
