    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant delivers linear torque through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via an M Variable Differential Lock. Critical preventive maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the double-VANOS system operates flawlessly. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing adaptable damping rates for various track or street conditions. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the mechanical integrity is robust, featuring a reinforced subframe and fresh bushings. This is a purist's spec, prioritizing mechanical synchronization and lateral grip over concours-level aesthetics.",
